rets mellomoppgj\u00f8r. Rammen er den samme \u2013 2,4 prosent.", "\u2013 Ogs\u00e5 i \u00e5r har vi bidratt til et ansvarlig oppgj\u00f8r ved \u00e5 ta hensyn til den konkurranseutsatte industrien. Dette til tross for at l\u00f8nnsveksten var vesentlig lavere enn prisveksten i 2016, slik at mange fikk redusert kj\u00f8pekraft, sier Vegard Einan, leder for YS privat."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "8e3b1d8a4fcc889d90c352363047f8309435047ef2b318a8bf19cdd5b5df10b7"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-14T20:51:34.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "LO og NHO er blitt enige om en ramme p\u00e5 2,4 prosent i v\u00e5rens l\u00f8nnsoppgj\u00f8r i privat sektor."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b05c2b005c5c2cfccc5ff39b88114350761b4174.jpg?59777fa3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "\u00c5rets l\u00f8nnsoppgj\u00f8r i boks -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "b05c2b005c5c2cfccc5ff39b88114350761b4174"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["lav", "oppgj\u00f8r", "prosent", "oppn\u00e5 enighet", "mars", "\u00e5rets l\u00f8nnsoppgj\u00f8r", "\u00e5rets", "\u00e5rets mellomoppgj\u00f8r", "enige"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["europa", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["skogen lund", "vegard einan", "gerd kristiansen", "k